title: The Depanneur
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, American, Bakery, Caribbean, Fusion, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A corner store and restaurant. Hosts a community of chefs in a supper club program called the Rusholme Park Supper Club. At least one of these meals each month is vegan. Holds two drop-in dinners per week, usually has a vegan option - best to check ahead. Store sells local produce.
